{"tid":1003912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"攀欄替模特兒拍照　健美先生商廈失足墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-02-01T04:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T05:17:18.000Z","uid":25345,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"39d717409dfda8a1cf375cd32df5451c38e5afc4","tid":1003912,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T04:57:45.000Z","msg":"死者姓江26歲，英文名阿Will，在墮樓大廈內一間健身中心做健身教練。《蘋果》聯絡到樓上另一間健身中心的黃姓職員，同時也是死者的舊同事。黃今早返工，已經發生墮樓事件，他向大廈保安員了解後，得悉死者竟然就是阿Will，感到非常突然。黃估計是意外：「自殺唔會，估計是意外，可能佢影相，響12樓平台爬出去，外面空間好窄㗎！」他估計事主失足墮樓。<br />\n<br />\n黃指，阿Will年約25歲，是freelance健身教練，本身有參加健美比賽，前兩日剛於澳門一項健美比賽中獲獎。黃形容，阿Will「有上進心、好nice」，由於他不時自拍上載到交友網站，黃估計他今次也是在12樓平台自拍時出意外。「嗰度有差唔多5呎多的欄杆，爬出去，外面空間好窄。」<br />\n<br />\n他在互聯網上自我介紹稱，有4年個人健身教練經驗，剛於前兩日，在GLOBAL CLASSIC澳門站邀請賽獲第4名，另外於2016奧林匹克先生亞洲香港賽獲亞軍、2016香港健美健身總會男子型體健美錦標賽第六名。他的fb內亦滿載健身比賽及生活照，其中一張合成相片顯示，他在2010年皮膚白滑，經過艱苦的操練，2016年即展現8件腹肌的健美身型。<br />\n<br />\n另外，他在學歷簡介中指出，中學於深水灣的南島中學畢業，再先後於清華大學商業/管理經濟學及英國曼徹斯特大學工商管理畢業。2013年起投身健身教練行列。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170817/large/1502944025_ad91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170817%2Flarge%2F1502944025_ad91.jpg&h=7b45a358&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ebab04bea4888c1549b7b61df7dcdb493b110e1","tid":1003912,"uid":15620,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T04:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e442027c6b1d81d542f970ee58cf060d0e98f31","tid":1003912,"uid":43721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T04:59:02.000Z","msg":"係咪睇過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1e0409de9ffdaa673048da8b58d4ca03ae4573","tid":1003912,"uid":49197,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T05:00:25.000Z","msg":"抵啦健身狗"},{"pid":"164d6bcf885e74c9ec105bf19bc2343041485c45","tid":1003912,"uid":118709,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T05:00:47.000Z","msg":"old news"},{"pid":"97e4ac193a485a5e4e046014770c9508ea5764c2","tid":1003912,"uid":154255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T05:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  POST完又POST <br />\nOLD NEWS <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60201649e27a8a517a390a4062e1142749950d62","tid":1003912,"uid":124107,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T05:06:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68467225087666bf878b83f38b78cd2bb135a067","tid":1003912,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T05:09:48.000Z","msg":"哂哂 又後生又大隻又型 本來可以狂食女"},{"pid":"e56fd707abeecbaeedb9344ef05b564ade90f90d","tid":1003912,"uid":8171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T05:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images4.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20091127083246/evchk/images/5/54/20091127162713_7eb9f76329f492873928f9f5222d0246.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages4.wikia.nocookie.net%2F__cb20091127083246%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F5%2F54%2F20091127162713_7eb9f76329f492873928f9f5222d0246.gif&h=d55668b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影相啫，做乜要噤搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e509843aa0cc19347ddb3d0fa0b54d8596470b","tid":1003912,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T05:16:47.000Z","msg":"做咩鬼今日咁多old news架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd1ed834c142ef1ee5425b6ae3f732af825f23e","tid":1003912,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T05:17:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">WASTED</span></strong>"}]}